# Time Complexity

Suppose

```java
for(int i = 1; i <= n; i++){

    for(int j = 1; j <= n; j++){

    }

}
```

Iterations

```
n × n
```

Time Complexity

```
O(n²)
```

Space Complexity

```
O(1)
```

### Triangle Pattern

```java
for(int i = 1; i <= n; i++){

    for(int j = 1; j <= i; j++){

    }

}
```

Total iterations

```
1 + 2 + 3 + ... + n

= n(n + 1) / 2
```

Time Complexity

```
O(n²)
```

